# pyenv
#   For a library or package, you might want to share your .python-version.
#   For an app, this should be excluded:
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if used with a windows machine, Pipfile.lock might not be portable.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock contains the resolved dependencies.
#   It's recommended to commit this file in applications, but not libraries.
#poetry.lock

